description: Andrey Vic is in a bit of a financial jam. His business is failing, and he’s willing to do whatever it takes to get a loan to save himself and his livelihood. Business partners Alexander Volkov and Dylan James are first-rate sharks, and they’re more than willing to help out Andrey, but only if he gives his ass to them as collateral first.
title: Dylan James And Alexander Volkov Double-Team Andrey Vic
